<prediction-of-dry-gas-water-content>
The achievable water content of the dry gas depends on:

- #strong[TEG purity]: higher purity achieves lower water dew points
- #strong[Temperature]: lower contactor temperature improves dehydration
- #strong[Number of stages]: more theoretical stages improve separation
- #strong[TEG circulation rate]: higher rates approach but never exceed the equilibrium limit

