= CO$""_2$ and Acid Gas Systems
<co_2-and-acid-gas-systems>
== Learning Objectives
<learning-objectives>
After reading this chapter, the reader will be able to:

+ Model CO$""_2$--water phase behavior using CPA with solvation
+ Predict the effect of impurities on CO$""_2$ phase boundaries
+ Apply CPA to CCS pipeline design and injection well analysis
